Xintong Jiang holds a BEng in Automation from Jiamusi University, Heilongjiang, China (graduated in 2025). He interned as a Backend Engineer at CCB Supply Chain Finance (June-August 2024), contributing to machine learning projects. Currently, he works as a Part-time Research Assistant at the Intelligent Mobility and Robotics Lab, University of New Brunswick, with research interests in autonomous control systems and multi-agent control.
